map = folium.Map(location=[location_y, location_x], zoom_start=12)

for n in df_seoul_hospital.index:
    name=df_seoul_hospital.loc[n, ""]
    address = df_seoul_hospital.loc[n, ""]
    popup = folium.Popup(f"{name}-{address}", max_width=50)
    location = [df_seoul_hospital.loc[n,""], df_seoul_hospital.loc[n,""]]
    
    folium.Marker(
        location = location,
        popup = popup,
    ).add_to(map)
    
map.save('index.html')
